Usage:

  1. Drop images and fill in (a) URL(s). First pic corresponds with first URL, ...
  2. Make sure you take a picture with contrasts (the more color shades, the better).
  3. click "Convert". Wait a bit and see your link, HTML-file and Qr-code.


Important:
Atleast one url must be placed here. The character | is not allowed
A website with "same-origin policy" won't work through our Augme site; a html-file to place on your site will be generated.
